These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, dog, rat, ferret, fish, mouse
The people use 6 different means of transport: train, car, bus, motorbike, roller, jet-ski
1. the person driving the train is the owner of the bird##1
2. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the person driving the train is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the roller##2
5. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
8. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the bus##1
9. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| Pet         | fish     | rat | bird | ferret | mouse      | dog |
| Transport   | motorbike | roller  | train    | jet-ski | bus | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: epic, zombie, fantasy, western, martial-arts, crime
There are 6 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, malaysian, russian, colombian, indian
 1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the mexican##1
 2. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the indian is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is the russian##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the colombian is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the colombian##1
10. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | western  | martial-arts | zombie   | crime | fantasy |
| Nationality   | malaysian | colombian | egyptian    | indian | mexican   | russian   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, punk, hip-hop, techno, pop
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: surfing, climbing, water-polo, sailing, tennis, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
4. the fan of hip-hop is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
6. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |    3    |       4       |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | techno | punk     | dubstep         | hip-hop       | pop     |
| Sport         | surfing | water-polo  | climbing | snowboarding | tennis | sailing |

