.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: epic, documentary, sports, martial-arts, time-travel, fantasy
The people use 6 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, snowmobile, bike, ship, subway
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
3. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching sports movies##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
8. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
9. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | documentary     | sports     | martial-arts | time-travel | fantasy |
| Transport     | subway    | quad-bike | snowmobile | bike  | ship       | scooter      |

