.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, satire, martial-arts, zombie, disaster, sports
The people use 6 different means of transport: subway, airplane, motorbike, bus, ship, tram
 1. the person driving the bus is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person driving the motorbike##2
 2. the person watching satire movies is the person driving the tram##1
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 7. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 8. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
11. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
12. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | zombie | family | sports    | martial-arts    | satire |
| Transport     | airplane         | subway       | motorbike  | bus | ship | tram   |

