 4. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 5. the fan of dubstep is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of blues is in an odd position##4
 7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 8. the fan of soul is the malaysian##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is on the far left or far right##3
10. the egyptian is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | d&b   | soul    | r&b    | blues  | pop   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | canadian | malaysian | mexican | nigerian | australian |

