.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-7::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  teacher, chef, bartender, coach, designer, accountant
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: swimming, skateboarding, rowing, water-polo, baseball, basketball
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is the accountant##1
 2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the coach##3
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the accountant##3
 4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the accountant##1
 6. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
 7. the chef is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 8. the bartender is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the teacher is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Job     | coach | chef     | designer | teacher  | bartender     | accountant |
| Sport   | skateboarding         | baseball | water-polo              | rowing | swimming | basketball |

