.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-8::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, 7up, fanta, mirinda, coffee
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: climbing, handball, ice-hockey, badminton, rugby, baseball
 1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person who's sport is climbing is in an odd position##4
11. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
12. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |    3     |       4       |     5      |      6       |
| Beverage   | cola | 7up     | juice | coffee         | mirinda        | fanta       |
| Sport      | ice-hockey       | badminton | climbing  | baseball | rugby | handball |

