.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-9::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, almond-milk, juice, tea, hot-chocolate
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, camping, reading, sudoku, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is camping##2
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4       |   5    |     6     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk       | sprite     | tea     | juice  | lemonade    |
| Hobby      | reading | board-games | drawing | camping | dancing | sudoku |

