 4. the person drinking juice is the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 9. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the roller##1
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage    | coffee | soy-milk | iced-tea | juice | 7up      | tea    |
| Transport   | roller       | airplane      | snowmobile     | taxi  | bus | helicopter |

