.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-20::.
There 6 different types of food: kale, orange, cucumber, pumpkin, peach, potato
The people have 6 different jobs:  journalist, manager, project-manager, photographer, mechanic, dressmaker
 1. the photographer is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
 2. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
 3. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 5. the dressmaker is on the right of the photographer##1
 6. the person eating kale is the mechanic##1
 7. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
 8. the project-manager is on the far right##1
 9. the journalist is between the person eating peach and the manager##2
10. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating potato##1
11. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
12. the photographer is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Food   | kale    | cucumber      | pumpkin  | peach  | potato           | orange  |
| Job    | mechanic | manager | journalist | photographer | dressmaker | project-manager |

 